[[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=how-it-works-block-0.title"},"Nodoku way"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=how-it-works-block-0.subTitle"},"Nodoku suggests a simple way of creating content-centric landing pages, using Markdown and Yaml"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=example-header-block-0.title"},"Here is an example"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=example-header-block-0.subTitle"},"Suppose you are creating a product landing page"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=example-result-header-block-0.subTitle"},"And here is the result"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=generated-with-nodoku-block-0.title"},"And Yes!<br><br>This <strong><em>whole site</em></strong> was generated with Nodoku!"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=generated-with-nodoku-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"Check out the source code of this page at <br><a href=\"https://github.com/epanikas/nodoku-demo-page\">https://github.com/epanikas/nodoku-demo-page</a>"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-header-block-0.title"},"Why you would like to give Nodoku a try"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-carousel-header-block-0.subTitle"},"The same cards can be presented as the <strong><em>Carousel</em></strong> component"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-carousel-header-block-0.h3"},"This is just a matter of skin configuration"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=languages-footer-block-0.subTitle"},"Nodoku allows for easy localization of the static site content"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=languages-footer-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"<a href=\"/readme/i18n\">Learn more about Nodoku localization capabilities</a>"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"CCTV is a set of libraries aiming at creating beautiful and responsive landing pages effortlessly."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.paragraphs.1"},"Nodoku uses <strong><em>Markdown</em></strong> file as content supplier, and a <strong><em>Yaml</em></strong> file as visual configurator."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"Nodoku is a framework on top of <strong><em>NextJS</em></strong>, <strong><em>React</em></strong> and <strong><em>Tailwind</em></strong>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.paragraphs.1"},"Nodoku is using the underlying NextJS capabilities of Server-Side-Rendering (SSR)."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.paragraphs.2"},"The Nodoku engine parses the supplied Markdown file into content blocks."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.paragraphs.3"},"Then it renders each block using the configuration provided in the Yaml file - called <em><strong>skin</strong></em>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"Concentrate on the subject of your product / service to highlight its advantages."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.paragraphs.1"},"Use your <em>favorite</em> text editor to create a content-rich MD (markdown) file,\nwithout worrying about presentation."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.paragraphs.2"},"Using content block delimeter - a Yaml code snippet -\nstructure the content file, so that it can be submitted to the Nodoku parser."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=example-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"create a Markdown content file, describing your product"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"id=product-1-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"Description of my product."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"id=product-1-block-0.paragraphs.1"},"And another line of description."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"id=product-1-block-0.paragraphs.2"},"<a href=\"https://www.freepik.com/free-photo/still-life-with-plants-deco_20734103.htm#fromView=search&amp;page=1&amp;position=0&amp;uuid=6672daf1-0fe9-4f7d-afb6-46705817ca8c\">image by Freepik</a>"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-0.paragraphs.0"},"Unlike Nodoku, the vast majority of site builders are using the so-called WYSIWYG (What You See Is What You Get) approach, when the site is being built gradually, by filling in the web-forms right on the visual elements."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-0.paragraphs.1"},"Even though this approach gives a very fast visual impression of your future page, it has a major drawback - it is very <strong><em>distracting</em></strong>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-0.paragraphs.2"},"Nodoku is suggesting a different approach - <strong><em>you create content first</em></strong>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-0.paragraphs.3"},"The content is created in a textual form in a Markdown file, and at this moment <em>nothing else matters</em>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-1.paragraphs.0"},"Nodoku promotes a strict separation between the content and the presentation, allowing for a great deal of flexibility, when one can be changed without affecting the other."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-1.paragraphs.1"},"This approach is illustrated by the fact that the content and the design are represented by different files - <strong><em>Markdown file</em></strong> for content, and <strong><em>Yaml file</em></strong> - called <em>skin</em> - for visual presentation."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-1.paragraphs.2"},"Keeping content and design concepts strictly separated allows for independent editing of both, without worrying about the impact that one might have on another."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-2.paragraphs.0"},"Nodoku has been designed from ground up keeping in mind the necessity of the content localization."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-2.paragraphs.1"},"The content in Nodoku is represented by a set of <strong><em>content blocks</em></strong>, each of which is a separated piece of content (usually a paragraph or a title)."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-2.paragraphs.2"},"The content becomes easily localizable, since each content block has its unique key."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-2.paragraphs.3"},"This key can naturally be used as a <strong><em>translation key</em></strong>, that can be integrated with the localization solution of your choice."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-2.paragraphs.4"},"Check out <a href=\"https://github.com/nodoku/nodoku-i18n\">nodoku-i18n</a> for more details."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-3.paragraphs.0"},"Each Nodoku component is carefully crafted such that it would be presented correctly on any browsing device."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-3.paragraphs.1"},"The currently available sets of Nodoku components, <a href=\"https://github.com/nodoku/nodoku-flowbite\"><strong><em>Nodoku-Flowbite</em></strong></a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/nodoku/nodoku-mambaui\"><strong><em>Nodoku-MambaUI</em></strong></a> based on <a href=\"https://flowbite.com/\">Flowbite</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mambaui.com/\">Mamba UI</a> set of visual blocks respectively, are all responsive <em>to provide the best user experience</em>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-3.paragraphs.2"},"The Nodoku skin - a Yaml file providing visual customization - is based on the Tailwind CSS styling engine, which gives large possibilities for responsive design tuning."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-4.paragraphs.0"},"A Nodoku page is organized as a <strong><em>set of rows</em></strong>, each row having one or more visual components."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-4.paragraphs.1"},"Such row-oriented layout gives a clear understanding of the structure of your page, and predictable visual element placement."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-4.paragraphs.2"},"By default, each row in a Nodoku page is using <strong><em>CSS grid</em></strong> to organize the row inner elements."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-4.paragraphs.3"},"However, the layout of a row can be switched to <strong><em>CSS flex</em></strong>, if required."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-4.paragraphs.4"},"This allows, depending on your particular requirements, adapt the layout that best suits your needs."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-5.paragraphs.0"},"Nodoku is using Server-Side Rendering, powered by the <a href=\"https://github.com/vercel/next.js\">NextJS</a> framework."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-5.paragraphs.1"},"All the Nodoku pages are pre-built in advance during the offline build process."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-5.paragraphs.2"},"This allows not only for the lightning fast page loading, but also for <strong><em>Search Engine Optimization</em></strong>, since each page is readily available, and can be scanned by the search engines easily."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-5.paragraphs.3"},"No Javascript code is required to be executed prior to page scanning by the web search engine."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-5.paragraphs.4"},"Consequently, the whole page naturally becomes <strong><em>SEO friendly</em></strong>."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-6.paragraphs.0"},"Nodoku framework is extensible by design, since it is <strong><em>the end user that controls the mapping</em></strong> between visual components and Yaml skin configuration."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-6.paragraphs.1"},"Nodoku is using the so-called <em>component provider</em> - a function that returns a visual component representation according to the Yaml skin file description."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-6.paragraphs.2"},"This implementation is responsible for the ultimate component rendering, using the theme and localization."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=advantages-block-6.paragraphs.3"},"Consequently, the end-user can easily extend the existing set of components by custom ones, as required."],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.images.0.url"},"{../images/postit-board.jpg}"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.images.0.alt"},"step-1"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.title"},"Step 1: <em>Think</em>"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.subTitle"},"Create content promoting your product or service as an <strong>MD file</strong>"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.callToActions.0.ctaUrl"},"/docs/getting-started"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.callToActions.0.ctaTitle"},"Get started"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.callToActions.1.ctaUrl"},"/docs/blog-article"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=nodoku-way-block-0.callToActions.1.ctaTitle"},"Learn more"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.title"},"CCTV"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.subTitle"},"my first projects  <br>static site generator"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.callToActions.0.ctaUrl"},"/docs/getting-started"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.callToActions.0.ctaTitle"},"Get started"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.callToActions.1.ctaUrl"},"/docs/blog-article"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=head-hero-block-0.callToActions.1.ctaTitle"},"Learn more"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.images.0.url"},"{../images/svg/Business_SVG.svg}"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"sectionName=what-is-it-block-0.images.0.alt"},"step-1"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"id=product-1-block-0.images.0.url"},"{../images/still-life-with-plants-deco.jpg}"],[{"language":"en","namespace":"cctv-landing","key":"id=product-1-block-0.images.0.alt"},"my-awesome-product"],[